summary: Just as the title says, it\'s an Apocrypha Player Home.
descriptionHtml: Just as the title says, it\'s an Apocrypha Player Home. It\'s a very simple one, simply containing a room with a bed, and a few chests. You can find the portal at the Summit of Apocrypha (where you defeat Miraak.) It\'s just a book teleporter, just as all of the other Apocrypha quests. All chests are non-respawnable. Requires Dragonborn.
author: dmcthunder999
